Established neighborhoods refer to those with more than one property; 
The 'zestimate' value is an estimated worth of a property, often used as a basis for comparison or valuation in real estate; 
Age range of properties is a measure of how old the oldest and youngest properties in a neighborhood are, which can be an indicator of neighborhood development and growth.

sql:
